{"tid":2210040,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【送中 29 天】朱凱廸：中共向每人派 2 律師 為「打爆 quota」阻家屬律師介入","createTime":"2020-09-20T06:10:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T06:11:22.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b4d0c5a4fc4a2c91b33cd9b8a5b6aab0b83b5e94","tid":2210040,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T06:10:42.000Z","msg":"朱凱廸今日在 FB 發文，引述《刑事訴訟法》第 33 條指，被扣留人可以找 1 至 2 名律師任辯護人。如果中共只派 1 名官方律師給被扣留人，就沒有理由拒絕家屬委託的律師：「所以，李家超做中共傳聲筒話每個被扣港人都選擇了 2 名官派律師，目的是『打爆個 quota』，等『家屬律師』冇位置介入」。<br />\n<br />\n朱凱廸認為，事件反映 12 港人極有可能不會在短期內釋放回港，「營救工作仍需努力」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD-29-%E5%A4%A9-%E6%9C%B1%E5%87%B1%E5%BB%B8-%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E5%90%91%E6%AF%8F%E4%BA%BA%E6%B4%BE-2-%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB-%E7%82%BA-%E6%89%93%E7%88%86-quota-%E9%98%BB%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%AC%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E4%BB%8B%E5%85%A5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD-29-%25E5%25A4%25A9-%25E6%259C%25B1%25E5%2587%25B1%25E5%25BB%25B8-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25B1%25E5%2590%2591%25E6%25AF%258F%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B4%25BE-2-%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB-%25E7%2582%25BA-%25E6%2589%2593%25E7%2588%2586-quota-%25E9%2598%25BB%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E4%25BB%258B%25E5%2585%25A5%2F&d=eCiXx0TsV7ZnsYjNRM2OmgDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=4efbb259\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD-29-%25E5%25A4%25A9-%25E6%259C%25B1%25E5%2587%25B1%25E5%25BB%25B8-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25B1%25E5%2590%2591%25E6%25AF%258F%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B4%25BE-2-%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB-%25E7%2582%25BA-%25E6%2589%2593%25E7%2588%2586-quota-%25E9%2598%25BB%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E4%25BB%258B%25E5%2585%25A5%2F&h=81518c0a\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD-29-%E5%A4%A9-%E6%9